# current.txt is the local Phase 9 bench-sweep artifact. Never committed;
# the gate test skips when it is absent so default `go test` does not
# require local benchmark generation.
#
# phase0.txt + metric2.txt ARE committed (closure-plan G.1): phase0.txt
# encodes the pre-summit baseline + per-workload waivers (forensically
# auditable via the recorded SHA); metric2.txt encodes the current
# measurement matched against it. Reviewer-gated updates only.
